Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.08,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9話 大家與面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌啊 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請吧 多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說讓你們多吃點 一臉得意地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我突然覺得涼颼颼地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啊 噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波個子大 就吃最大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說波波個子最大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對啊 我變成個子最大的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好吃 好吃啊面碼!  -太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會給我一個最什麼樣的呢 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給雪集一個葡萄乾最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼 我希望你能直接告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 紙 紙 筆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這樣面碼就能表達了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?寫不出來啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記上你明明寫了字的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?這不是有墨水的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我 再給我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子 輕點...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼困得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 身上好像一點力氣都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...沒有生我們的氣 原諒了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是原諒了我們還不好說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?可是...如果還在生氣 怎麼會為我們做蒸麵包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為無法原諒我們 為了報復才出現在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是有可能的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不過話說回來 能寫字的話 早點寫不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對啊 如果那樣的話早就能交流了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不會一直不信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為仁太和面碼都少根筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 雖然他一直說讓我們相信面碼的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-實際上他只是想獨佔面碼而已  -啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川 安城 工資要好好攢著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做出花火來 絕對...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要讓面碼成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧得那麼歡 當然會累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家正打算做花火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會開心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯?你沒睡著啊  -謝謝你仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就...足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼 跑那麼快很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.11,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:06:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-誒?面碼在跑嗎?那我也要跑!  -哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我~面碼~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.65,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法 無法原諒喜歡仁太的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣 我還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不甘心啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-對不起!  -啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週能和我換換班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換班?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜四橋那邊有工程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為日薪比較高 我想過去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:43.20,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!呐呐 你聽我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 終於跑膩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您好  -嗯?你們是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我妻子 芽衣子的母親與山先生聯絡過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是伯母...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 伯父不反對花火的事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活在過去之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子發生了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後她的時間就靜止不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把她帶回現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能讓她再想起那些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雪集?  -松雪君...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母的心情...這樣說可能有些自己為是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經很喜歡您的女兒芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為芽衣子做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也還活在過去之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到你會做出那麼遜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點都沒變啊 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了面碼 什麼都做得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒關係  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你相信 就沒關係 讓面碼成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明一直那麼放不下面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在通過宿海 明明能和面碼交談的 可是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要通過宿海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 要去打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今晚會很晚 所以想先把面碼送回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼在旁邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不想在家裡憋著 我去哪她都要跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是哦 我想和大家一起加油哦  -是是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-面碼...  -嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮還是那麼長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 其實 已經長得和我們一樣大了呢 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會喜歡這種醜女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多 基本上 能算是好看吧...可愛系?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴啊白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就是差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像在看獨角戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 其實不是獨角戲呢 因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做給你們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能讓你們碰火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們要不要幫我做些簡單的活兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這是要從竹筒裡冒出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還是紅色多點比較可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的和給人的印象不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡點火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 那這裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那只是裝飾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了上發射台的時候搬運起來比較容易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.90,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害 好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面碼 危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬆手啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在跳到你背上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊?面碼啊 饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波~波波波波~波波~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...我明明看不見 他卻能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前贏不了 現在也一樣 贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買點果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-喲 你救到我了  -啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你跑了出來 我也出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快叫出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼就在旁邊 我相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我卻看不見面碼 也不能和她說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再見一次面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼只有宿海能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為面碼喜歡的是宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海喜歡的也是面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認輸了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明又開始叫他仁太了 又換成宿海了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊 你這種好像把人看透了一樣的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看透的也就只有你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的境遇相似的人同病相憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要和你這種性格惡劣的人相似
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的那件事 我可是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?之前?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說我們要不要試著交往下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的對男人沒抗性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的中段踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 什麼叫漂亮的中段踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼笑 我真的嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼意外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我燃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太 anaru的布偶不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 突然就跑回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫反復無常啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說 就算面碼真的在仁太那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現了願望的話面碼不就消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 啊 到兼職的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 面碼你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和波波在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想留在這 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然願意了非常願意 超級願意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太能瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心...對吧...面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 那個我看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.40,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.01,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生用雙截棍戰鬥的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季校服...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.98,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初還以為是夏日的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.14,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說還要出新作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.33,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新作?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已經...開始穿冬季校服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香港 和老師打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.49,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你好)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 好厲害啊 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是仁太家裡的筆記本不能寫 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多寫點吧 再多聊點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.70,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(好啊 聊些什麼呢)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 那個...
